title: Daz3D - Miu2 for Genesis 3 Females
description:
Daz3D - Miu2 for Genesis 3 Female(s)


This product is a character set for Genesis 3 Female.
The set is based on Miu for V3 and uses the Genesis 3 Female UV Maps and morphs along with the custom morphs used in MamiV7
This product has materials for Iray and 3delight.

Hair used in promo pic is Sally Hair from DAZ

This torrent contains a custom generated DIM file that can be used with the DAZ Install Manager.
